data.description: Gorgeous canal front property in the Sunrise area. This beautiful 3/2 home has impact windows and doors and a screened in patio/pool area. Stove, dryer, water heater, and heating are gas powered and there is a gas connection outside that can be used for a generator. No HOA restrictions.
